  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >⚠️DISCLAIMER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Vengeance has a small but passionate community. Finding a match with other players can sometimes take time — but don’t worry! The game features full bot support for all modes, so you can always jump straight into the action.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>If you’re unsure whether this suits your playstyle, try out the free Demo before purchasing.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play Fast Play The Past</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/384960/extras/4da6345ac7b5486cbfb280388228e882.poster.avif?t=1770641471\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/384960/extras/4da6345ac7b5486cbfb280388228e882.webm?t=1770641471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/384960/extras/4da6345ac7b5486cbfb280388228e882.mp4?t=1770641471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vengeance is an old-modern-school shooter — a paradox that just works.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forget microtransactions, loot boxes, or endless grind. Vengeance brings back the raw, skill-based fun of classic shooters from the mid-2000s.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you loved fast-paced online shooters from that era, you’ll feel right at home here.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Small Chaotic Maps</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/384960/extras/f489f03938761ed9201ff6c44553a9ea.poster.avif?t=1770641471\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/384960/extras/f489f03938761ed9201ff6c44553a9ea.webm?t=1770641471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/384960/extras/f489f03938761ed9201ff6c44553a9ea.mp4?t=1770641471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every map in Vengeance is designed for speed and intensity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No waiting, no downtime — respawn instantly and get back into the fight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With five compact, chaotic maps, expect nonstop action and heart-pounding close encounters.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Your Playstyle Your Weapon</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/384960/extras/49de6d829f82344bd8d6ebebb58eae5a.poster.avif?t=1770641471\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/384960/extras/49de6d829f82344bd8d6ebebb58eae5a.webm?t=1770641471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/384960/extras/49de6d829f82344bd8d6ebebb58eae5a.mp4?t=1770641471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick from over 20 unique weapons — from submachine guns to shotguns and everything in between.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each weapon has its own personality, recoil, and rhythm. Find your favorite and master it.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >No Players No Problem</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/384960/extras/1abb1bf78adf4c062eb8e25e14f214a4.poster.avif?t=1770641471\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/384960/extras/1abb1bf78adf4c062eb8e25e14f214a4.webm?t=1770641471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/384960/extras/1abb1bf78adf4c062eb8e25e14f214a4.mp4?t=1770641471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can’t find a match? Jump in with fully supported bots.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn ranks, unlock new weapons, and progress through the game — all without needing real opponents.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAME EDITIONS </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/384960/extras/37631f37ca6b40d4e0bedbf5a48c5177.avif?t=1769287518\" /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Not Convinced?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try the free Demo version of Vengeance!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It includes all maps and two weapons — the M4 and P350 — so you can experience the gameplay before committing.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >⚠️DISCLAIMER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Vengeance has a small but passionate community. Finding a match with other players can sometimes take time — but don’t worry! The game features full bot support for all modes, so you can always jump straight into the action.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>If you’re unsure whether this suits your playstyle, try out the free Demo before purchasing.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play Fast Play The Past</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/384960/extras/4da6345ac7b5486cbfb280388228e882.poster.avif?t=1770641471\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/384960/extras/4da6345ac7b5486cbfb280388228e882.webm?t=1770641471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/384960/extras/4da6345ac7b5486cbfb280388228e882.mp4?t=1770641471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vengeance is an old-modern-school shooter — a paradox that just works.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forget microtransactions, loot boxes, or endless grind. Vengeance brings back the raw, skill-based fun of classic shooters from the mid-2000s.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you loved fast-paced online shooters from that era, you’ll feel right at home here.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Small Chaotic Maps</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/384960/extras/f489f03938761ed9201ff6c44553a9ea.poster.avif?t=1770641471\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/384960/extras/f489f03938761ed9201ff6c44553a9ea.webm?t=1770641471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/384960/extras/f489f03938761ed9201ff6c44553a9ea.mp4?t=1770641471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every map in Vengeance is designed for speed and intensity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No waiting, no downtime — respawn instantly and get back into the fight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With five compact, chaotic maps, expect nonstop action and heart-pounding close encounters.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Your Playstyle Your Weapon</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/384960/extras/49de6d829f82344bd8d6ebebb58eae5a.poster.avif?t=1770641471\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/384960/extras/49de6d829f82344bd8d6ebebb58eae5a.webm?t=1770641471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/384960/extras/49de6d829f82344bd8d6ebebb58eae5a.mp4?t=1770641471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick from over 20 unique weapons — from submachine guns to shotguns and everything in between.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each weapon has its own personality, recoil, and rhythm. Find your favorite and master it.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >No Players No Problem</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/384960/extras/1abb1bf78adf4c062eb8e25e14f214a4.poster.avif?t=1770641471\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/384960/extras/1abb1bf78adf4c062eb8e25e14f214a4.webm?t=1770641471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/384960/extras/1abb1bf78adf4c062eb8e25e14f214a4.mp4?t=1770641471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can’t find a match? Jump in with fully supported bots.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn ranks, unlock new weapons, and progress through the game — all without needing real opponents.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAME EDITIONS </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/384960/extras/37631f37ca6b40d4e0bedbf5a48c5177.avif?t=1769287518\" /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Not Convinced?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try the free Demo version of Vengeance!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It includes all maps and two weapons — the M4 and P350 — so you can experience the gameplay before committing.</p>",
